    "course_title": "PROSEMINAR IN NURSING RESEARCH",
    "description": "Focus on professional development and socialization to the role of nurse scientist. Discussion emphasizes career development planning including traditional and alternative roles for PhD-prepared nurses, and current and emerging topics of importance to nursing science. The planned and ongoing research of graduate students and faculty in nursing will be featured as relevant.",
